This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation and reconstruction using deep neural networks. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it involves training and fine-tuning deep neural networks. Additionally, it may be relevant to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with MRI data, and the neural networks used may involve some form of natural language processing (cs.NE) for interpreting the data.
